Arsenal legend, Paul Merson, has predicted the outcomes of Premier League matchday 32 fixtures. Manchester City will host Liverpool at the Etihad Stadium on Sunday, while Leicester City will face Crystal Palace at the King Power Stadium. Everton will face Manchester United at Goodison Park on Saturday and Arsenal will host Brighton at Emirates Stadium. Providing his predictions, Merson was quoted by Sportskeeda as saying: Newcastle United 1-2 Wolves
Everton 2-1 Manchester United
Watford 2-2 Leeds United
Southampton 1-1 Chelsea
Arsenal 2-0 Brighton
Aston Villa 1-1 Tottenham Hotspur
Leicester City 2-2 Crystal Palace
Norwich City 2-2 Burnley
Brentford 1-1 West Ham United
Man City 2-2 Liverpool.